import Autocomplete from '@material-ui/lab/Autocomplete'

export default function StateTextFields() {
    const [name, setName] = React.useState('Cat in the Hat')

        setName(event.target.value)

                autoComplete="off"

                    {...defaultProps}
                    id="disable-clo/se-on-select"

    )
}
